twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/ritujoon2j/status/2050917191198056456", "text": "We booked a Stayvista property in Munnar from Airbnb for \u20b936k. \n\nFrom the start, there were many issues: leeches, cockroaches, a non-working gas stove, fungus on curtains, damaged non-stick utensils in the kitchen, and flickering lights. It has been the worst experience. We booked for 2 days but are leaving today.\n\nWhen we contacted Airbnb support, they said we lacked enough evidence of a bad experience, would follow whatever the host says, and offered only a \u20b91500 refund.\n\nWorst experience with Airbnb customer support. If you book from Airbnb, don\u2019t expect any support if things go wrong.\n\ndon\u2019t ever book this property in Munnar. The house is full of leeches. Avoid Stayvista or Airbnb from now on. \ud83d\ude1e\ud83d\ude1e\ud83d\ude1e\n@AirbnbHelp @Airbnb_in @Airbnb @bchesky @amanpreet_bajaj", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 228, "replyCount": 104, "likeCount": 770, "quoteCount": 12, "viewCount": 112730, "createdAt": "Sun May 03 12:35:37 +0000 2026", "lang": "en", "bookmarkCount": 58, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2050917191198056456", "displayTextRange": [0, 274], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "ritujoon2j", "url": "https://x.com/ritujoon2j", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/ritujoon2j", "id": "969834700545101824", "name": "Ritu Joon", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1957709242661761025/KTckHQOY_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/969834700545101824/1762970061", "description": "", "location": "Haryana | Bangalore", "followers": 5183, "following": 1861, "status": "", "canDm": true, "canMediaTag": true, "createdAt": "Sat Mar 03 07:19:46 +0000 2018", "entities": {"description": {"urls": []}, "url": {}}, "fastFollowersCount": 0, "favour